<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Kopiku Moses</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f5f5f5;
      color: #333;
    }header {
  background: #3e2723;
  color: white;
  padding: 20px;
  text-align: center;
}

nav {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  background: #5d4037;
}

nav a {
  color: white;
  padding: 15px 20px;
  text-decoration: none;
}

nav a:hover {
  background: #8d6e63;
}

.hero {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 60px 20px;
  background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509042239860-f550ce710b93') no-repeat center/cover;
  color: white;
}

.hero h1 {
  font-size: 48px;
}

.container {
  padding: 40px 20px;
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: auto;
}

.menu {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
  gap: 20px;
}

.card {
  background: white;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

footer {
  background: #3e2723;
  color: white;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 15px;
}

button {
  background: #6d4c41;
  color: white;
  border: none;
  padding: 10px 15px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  cursor: pointer;
}

button:hover {
  background: #8d6e63;
}

  </style>
</head>
<body><header>
  <h1>Kopiku Moses</h1>
  <p>Nikmati kopi terbaik dengan cita rasa khas</p>
</header><nav>
  <a href="#home">Home</a>
  <a href="#menu">Menu</a>
  <a href="#about">Tentang</a>
  <a href="#contact">Kontak</a>
</nav><section class="hero" id="home">
  <h1>Selamat Datang</h1>
  <p>Kopi hangat, suasana nyaman, cerita tak terlupakan</p>
</section><section class="container" id="menu">
  <h2>Menu Kami</h2>
  <div class="menu">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Espresso</h3>
      <p>Kopi hitam pekat dengan rasa kuat</p>
      <p><strong>Rp 15.000</strong></p>
      <button onclick="order('Espresso')">Pesan</button>
    </div><div class="card">
  <h3>Cappuccino</h3>
  <p>Perpaduan kopi, susu, dan foam lembut</p>
  <p><strong>Rp 20.000</strong></p>
  <button onclick="order('Cappuccino')">Pesan</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <h3>Latte</h3>
  <p>Kopi susu dengan rasa creamy</p>
  <p><strong>Rp 22.000</strong></p>
  <button onclick="order('Latte')">Pesan</button>
</div>

  </div>
</section><section class="container" id="about">
  <h2>Tentang Kami</h2>
  <p>Kopiku Moses adalah tempat nongkrong yang menghadirkan kopi berkualitas tinggi dengan suasana yang nyaman dan modern.</p>
</section><section class="container" id="contact">
  <h2>Kontak</h2>
  <p>Instagram: @kopikumoses</p>
  <p>WhatsApp: 08xxxxxxxxxx</p>
</section><footer>
  <p>&copy; 2026 Kopiku Moses. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer><script>
  function order(menu) {
    alert('Kamu memesan: ' + menu);
  }
</script></body>
</html>
